videos.description: Garrison Brooks spins before knocking down a tough fadeaway jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Brooks gets off-balanced fadeaway to fall) 2020/12/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brooks gets off-balanced fadeaway to fall

videos.description: Matt Coleman III drives and fakes out UNC's Day'Ron Sharpe for the open lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Coleman adjusts midair for easy layup) 2020/12/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coleman adjusts midair for easy layup

videos.description: Matt Coleman turns the corner and accelerates to the rim, readjusting around a help defender to drop in a stylish reverse layup for Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Texas' Coleman puts in smooth reverse layup) 2020/12/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Coleman puts in smooth reverse layup

videos.description: Matt Coleman II drives to the basket then uses a James Harden-like step-back move to sink the go-ahead bucket as Texas goes on to defeat North Carolina 69-67.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Texas' Coleman nails game-winner vs. UNC to win Maui Invitational) 2020/12/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Coleman nails game-winner vs. UNC to win Maui Invitational
